title: Code.ILLEGAL_POLLING_TIME is not compatible with gRPC Client <=5.0.2
description: Code.ILLEGAL_PILLING_TIME is introduced in rocketmq-proto 2.0.1, which is integrated by gRPC client 5.0.3, so it is not compatible with the older client.
description_text: Code.ILLEGAL_PILLING_TIME is introduced in rocketmq-proto 2.0.1, which is integrated by gRPC client 5.0.3, so it is not compatible with the older client.
